data.meta_description: c. 850/855 – 5 or 23 November 911). Member of the Hunfriding dynasty.  Duke of Swabia and Duke of Alamannia from 909 until his death. He also held the titles of Margrave of Raetia Curiensis and Count in the Thurgau and Baar.  Burchard was the son of Adalbert II the Illustrious, Count of Thurgau, and his wife Judith of...
